ZH: 这家医院提供了非常好的医疗服务。
EN: This hospital provides excellent medical services.

ZH: 我们需要去学校的图书馆还书。
EN: We need to return the books to the library at school.

ZH: 这个院子很大，可以种很多花。
EN: This courtyard is very big, so we can plant a lot of flowers.

ZH: 医院门口停了一辆救护车。
EN: An ambulance is parked at the entrance of the hospital.

ZH: 院子里有一条小狗在玩耍。
EN: There is a puppy playing in the courtyard.

ZH: 我们学校的老师大多在办公室。
EN: Most of our school teachers are in the office.

ZH: 我们去医院看望了生病的同学。
EN: We visited our sick classmate in the hospital.

ZH: 院长宣布了学校明天放假的消息。
EN: The dean announced that the school will be closed tomorrow.

ZH: 我们在院子里烧了一堆篝火。
EN: We lit a bonfire in the courtyard.

ZH: 医院里的病人都需要接受治疗。
EN: All the patients in the hospital need treatment.

ZH: 我们选了一个安静的地方在院子里做家庭作业。
EN: We found a quiet spot in the courtyard to do our homework.

ZH: 最好的医院应该提供高品质的医疗设施。
EN: The best hospitals should provide high-quality medical facilities.

ZH: 学校的校长跟老师们开了一个会。
EN: The school principal held a meeting with the teachers.

ZH: 我们院子里有很多果树，所以每年都有很多水果吃。
EN: There are a lot of fruit trees in our courtyard, so we have plenty of fruit to eat every year.

ZH: 这间医院是我们城市最好的医疗中心之一。
EN: This hospital is one of the best medical centers in our city.

ZH: 医院里有位年轻的医生给我做检查。
EN: A young doctor in the hospital examined me.

ZH: 我们院子里的草坪需要修剪。
EN: The lawn in our courtyard needs to be trimmed.

ZH: 她是医院的护士，每天都在帮助病人。
EN: She is a nurse in the hospital and helps patients every day.

ZH: 学校的图书馆里有很多有趣的书籍。
EN: The school library has a lot of interesting books.

ZH: 我去医院拿药，排了很长时间的队。
EN: I went to the hospital to get medicine and waited in line for a long time.
